ActFarm Income Protection Act
SubjectOrder Providing Financial Assistance to Producers in Nova Scotia, Prince Edward Island and Newfoundland and Labrador
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Agriculture and Agri-Food Canada to enter into AGREEMENTS with NOVA SCOTIA, PRINCE EDWARD ISLAND and NEWFOUNDLAND AND LABRADOR in order to provide federal contributions of up to $3.66 million to assist producers affected by Hurricane Fiona in 2022.
